{"tid":1187482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家關心下身邊朋友","createTime":"2019-06-05T16:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T05:01:24.000Z","uid":63821,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b72b0ac96abc1260c3638c021abd927836da8f33","tid":1187482,"uid":63821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"每個人身邊有唔同「功能」嘅朋友，有啲你會同佢討論政治，有啲你會同佢傾訴感情問題。<br />\n我想講嘅係，6月9號唔該除咗好直覺咁搵第一類朋友一齊出嚟之外，都可以問下第二類朋友有冇興趣一齊去。<br />\n<br />\n我都係上個禮拜睇返自己中學嘅聯署名單先發現平時唔係特別熱衷於政治嘅friend都有簽到。於是第二日就膽粗粗PM問佢有冇興趣去。結果發現佢唔係好清楚6月9號嘅活動詳情，又驚遲到早走唔方便。（留意返，佢係清楚逃犯條例做乜，但只係唔知遊行係點樣嘅一回事）解釋清楚之後就成功叫多個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(希望到時唔好畀人甩底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要努力將呢類型嘅朋友挖出嚟呀，其實好多時係差一個人踢一踢佢哋（尤其有啲人做乜都要有friend陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），只要問多聲就會多個人出嚟㗎啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227031dbfd0ba818a74023f72720737fd853fac8","tid":1187482,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事關香港歷史之重大變局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想借大家少少位用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家可以原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOPvJL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOPvJL6.png&h=344452d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止惡法！為時未晚！<br />\n<br />\n留意返由於預計示威人數好多，民陣已經將起點改咗喺維園！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百國聯軍助陣！感謝海外港人為香港人嘅未來而作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG0SmhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG0SmhW.png&h=5d5fe630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>愛因斯坦 (Albert Einstein)：「The world will not be destoryed by those who do evil, but by these who watch them without doing anything.(這個世界不會被那些作惡多端的人毀滅，而是冷眼旁觀、選擇保持緘默的人)」；鄭有傑(導演):「良心的沉默是邪惡的幫兇。」<br />\n<br />\n好多時歷史中嘅轉折位都係由表面上微不足道嘅小事/小人物而形成嘅，所以我地更加唔可以睇小自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=f510f5bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全球聯署、白宮聯署、學界、各行各業、宗教、地區/ 海外港人等等）反送中聯署合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY%2Fhtmlview&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=007f3999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview</a>"},{"pid":"29e6b4261dfda1ff6b76ed642fc799fe16bb44ff","tid":1187482,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae41896923e58888f27ea2a69f03dcd92b6f6eb","tid":1187482,"uid":63821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}